# uv.lock pins wheel URLs to whatever index uv is configured with locally
# (e.g. pypi-proxy.dev.databricks.com), which the Databricks Apps build network
# can't reach -> "error installing packages". Apps deploys use requirements.txt;
# never commit the lock.
uv.lock
